!!! 5

%html
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}
    :css
      label { font-weight: bold; }
  %body
    %p Welcome to the site. Please select the following link to start.
    %p
      = @default
    %p
      = link_to @url, @url
    %p
      = @add_text
    %p<
      If you do not have a GINA ID to log in to the site, please select the 
      Sign-up link.  On the signup page, enter your first/last name and your
      email address.  The Username can be any login text you wish or it can
      be your email or google account name. Enter the Password you want and
      then re-enter it in the Password confirmation field so it can be
      verified. Finaly select the Create User button to create your account.
    %p<
      If you forget your password, you can select the Forgotten Password?
      link.  Enter your email address and an email will be sent to you with
      instructions on how to reset your password.
